            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Ah I didn't realise it would go through a temporary variable.\n\nI don't really have an opinion if it should be a general feature. It seems a fairly niche feature so it probably isn't worth a lot of complication. But if it can be done simply it might be worthwhile.  I imagine it probably can be done fairly simply.",
